bio:
Extensive multi-sector global procurement background spanning over 25 years and is a Fellow of the Chartered Institute of Procurement and Supply (CIPS) and was the first in procurement globally to attain the Accredited Counter Fraud Technician in Procurement Fraud (ACFTech) with The Chartered Institute of Public Finance & Accountancy (CIPFA).

Committed to raising the profile of procurement fraud globally in both the Public and Private sectors through specialist prevention training and education through to investigation.
